Compatibility section

Note: Not all reactions will work or produce useable output due to the nature of the game. For example, size for armor does matter and the original mod is in terms of size intended for the name-giving beardy alcoholics.

Line 921: New Genesis (Volume II)
Line 924: The Aeramore Expansion
Line 22671: Dark Ages V: War & Mythos

Mod: New Genesis (Volume II)
Instructions: Load The Creation Forge after the mod (lower in the load order). Nothing else to do.
